        },
        "subject": "LU-3285 mdc: Data-on-MDT bugfixes",
        "message": "LU-3285 mdc: Data-on-MDT bugfixes\n\nPatch includes fixes found during DoM testing:\n- DoM lock don't change lock start/end from LOV\n- fix cl_object_layout_get() return values and checks\n- remove outdated invalid code from osc_object_ast_clear()\n- move -L option handling in lfs.c to handle it\n  alphabetically\n- fix lod_use_default_striping() to don't initialize OSP\n  objects for DOM layout\n\nTest-Parameters: mdssizegb=20 testlist=sanity-dom,dom-performance,racer\nSigned-off-by: Mikhal Pershin <mike.pershin@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I33e27c738028ecf18266a8591bc0fdd8ef430940\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/dom"
    }
